import React from "react"; function Collection({ name, health, damage, armor, bot_class, catchphrase, avatar_url, created_at, updated_at}) { return (
Name: {name}
Health: {health}
Damage: {damage}
Armor: {armor}
Class: {bot_class}
Catch{catchphrase}
{avatar_url}
{created_at}
{updated_at}
{/* {amount} */}
); } export default Collection;
